---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Relocation Guides & Articles
description: Expert guides for relocating from California to Phoenix. Tax comparisons, neighborhood guides, school information, and insider tips.
permalink: /blog/
---

<section class="page-header">
    <h1>Relocation Guides</h1>
    <p>Expert insights to help you navigate your California-to-Phoenix move</p>
</section>

<section class="section">
    <div class="posts-grid">
        {%- for post in collections.posts -%}
        <article class="post-card">
            <div class="post-card-image">
                {% if post.data.image %}
                <img src="{{ post.data.image }}" alt="{{ post.data.title }}">
                {% else %}
                <span class="post-card-category">{{ post.data.category or "Guide" }}</span>
                {% endif %}
            </div>
            <div class="post-card-content">
                <div class="post-card-meta">
                    <time datetime="{{ post.date | htmlDateString }}">{{ post.date | shortDate }}</time>
                    <span>•</span>
                    <span>{{ post.content | readingTime }}</span>
                </div>
                <h3><a href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a></h3>
                <p>{{ post.data.excerpt or post.content | excerpt }}</p>
                <a href="{{ post.url }}" class="read-more">Read More →</a>
            </div>
        </article>
        {%- endfor -%}
    </div>
    
    {% if collections.posts.length == 0 %}
    <p style="text-align: center; color: var(--color-gray-light);">No posts yet. Check back soon!</p>
    {% endif %}
</section>

<section class="cta-section">
    <div class="cta-inner">
        <h2>Have Questions About Relocating?</h2>
        <p>Our team has helped hundreds of California families make the move to Phoenix. Get personalized answers to your specific situation.</p>
        <a href="/contact/" class="btn btn-primary">Ask Us Anything</a>
    </div>
</section>
